%20comparing%20myself%20to%20others%20sucked%20all%20the%20energy%20from%20me%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20goal.%20My%20relationship%20with%20social%20media%20turned%20toxic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20lockdowns%20in%202020%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20post%20about%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffunko-pop-sends-plastic-figurines-to-dump-excess-inventory-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFunko%20Pop%3C%2Fa%3E%20collection.%20I%20absolutely%20love%20those%20little%20figures%20and%20probably%20have%20about%20500%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20before%2C%20this%20felt%20authentically%20%3Cem%3Eme%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20started%20posting%20about%20Disney%20at%20that%20time%2C%20too.%20Before%20I%20knew%20it%2C%20I'd%20created%20a%20little%20community%20with%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fblakespopnook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20joined%20TikTok%20in%20early%202021%2C%20and%20my%20follower%20count%20ballooned%20as%20I%20found%20my%20niche%20%E2%80%94%20what%20I%20call%20%26quot%3Bfandom%20lifestyle.%26quot%3B%20I%20once%20gained%205%2C000%20followers%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c390c539-dc14-4d99-b5aa-eb45695b5fc2%5C%22%3EInfluencing%20grew%20into%20more%20than%20my%20side%20hustle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20following%20steadily%20grew%2C%20I%20still%20viewed%20content%20creation%20as%20my%20hobby%20%E2%80%94%20not%20my%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20changed%20in%20February%202023%2C%20when%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20design%20job.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20I%20had%20about%20400%2C000%20followers%20on%20TikTok%20and%20around%2020%2C000%20on%20Instagram.%20I'd%20made%20some%20money%20by%20doing%20brand%20deals%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20until%20I%20was%20out%20of%20work%20that%20I%20fully%20embraced%20content%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-become-an-influencer-instagram-tiktok-youtube-snapchat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20a%20living%20as%20a%20social-media%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20once%20seemed%20impossible%20for%20me.%20But%20I'm%20actually%20supporting%20myself%20better%20now%20than%20when%20I%20was%20salaried.%20I%20still%20get%20some%20graphic-design%20freelance%20work%20on%20the%20side%2C%20but%20being%20an%20influencer%20is%20my%20main%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20post%20content%20almost%20every%20day%20to%20Instagram%2C%20TikTok%2C%20or%20both.%20I%20average%20one%20to%20two%20dozen%20posts%20per%20week%2C%20not%20counting%20my%20IG%20stories.%20For%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40blakespopnook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20every%20few%20weeks%2C%20but%20I'm%20hoping%20to%20post%20there%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20share%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20myself%20at%20Disneyland%20(rocking%20Disney%20merch%2C%20of%20course)%2C%20unboxing%20toys%2C%20and%20occasionally%20hunting%20for%20hard-to-find%20Disney%20products%20in%20stores.%20Most%20of%20my%20videos%20are%20at%20least%20a%20minute%20long%20because%20they%20are%20easier%20to%20monetize%20at%20that%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20creator%2C%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20my%20income%20comes%20from%20brand%20deals%2C%20which%20come%20with%20size%20and%20consistency%20%E2%80%94%20in%20posts%20and%20with%20my%20brand.%20I've%20worked%20with%20Mattel%2C%20Uniqlo%2C%20and%20even%20Disney%20itself.%20The%20type%20of%20campaign%20and%20length%20vary.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20key%20is%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20brands%20that%20reach%20out%20are%20a%20good%20fit%20so%20that%20partnerships%20feel%20organic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20my%20money%20comes%20from%20TikTok%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-on-youtube-millennial-financial-freedom-wealth-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20content%20monetization%20rate%20seems%20to%20constantly%20shift%2C%20though%20YouTube%20has%20consistently%20paid%20me%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221879%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blake%20Silva%203%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68308c9bca50259add4ce69d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221409%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESilva%20says%20brand%20deals%2C%20like%20this%20one%20with%20Lola%20Blankets%2C%20make%20up%20a%20solid%20chunk%20of%20his%20income.%3Cp%3EBlake%20Silva%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20day-to-day%20schedule%20varies%20dramatically.%20I%20live%20about%2025%20miles%20from%20Disneyland%20and%20usually%20make%20it%20there%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week.%20When%20I'm%20not%20at%20Disney%2C%20I%20might%20be%20editing%20videos%2C%20checking%20which%20videos%20got%20traction%2C%20or%20catching%20up%20on%20comments%2C%20messages%2C%20and%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20gotten%20so%20busy%20that%20I%20just%20signed%20with%20an%20agency%20to%20handle%20some%20of%20those%20tasks.%20I%20hope%20that%20will%20help%20me%20focus%20on%20my%20strengths%20and%20take%20my%20business%20to%20the%20next%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228bb86c01-531a-4372-9aee-e8b691593037%5C%22%3EMy%20advice%3F%20Be%20your%20authentic%20self%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20life%20as%20a%20creator%20is%20extremely%20fulfilling.%20I've%20had%20experiences%20I%20never%20even%20dreamed%20of%2C%20like%20getting%20behind-the-scenes%20tours%20of%20filming%20locations%2C%20invites%20to%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-cruise-line-expanding-new-ships-private-destination-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney%20cruise%20ships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20meeting%20Jim%20Cummings%2C%20who%20voiced%20my%20beloved%20Winnie%20the%20Pooh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%