%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-delays-work-marriage-children-homebuying-delayed-development-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20holding%20off%20on%20reaching%2C%20along%20with%20their%20first%20romantic%20relationships%20and%20entering%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20are%20waiting%20because%20of%20personal%20choice%2C%20others%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-house-prices-student-debt-childcare-inflation-interest-rates-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20realities%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20limiting%20what%20they%20can%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosrowshahi%20also%20said%20that%20the%20shift%20away%20from%20driving%20among%20young%20people%20marks%20a%20cultural%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20many%20young%20people%20have%20gotten%20their%20driver's%20licenses%20as%20soon%20as%20they're%20old%20enough%20to.%20Podcast%20host%20Nilay%20Patel%20said%20that%20he%20got%20his%20license%20at%2015-and-a-half%20while%20growing%20up%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20goal%20in%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Khosrowshahi%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20represented%20freedom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20started%20offering%20a%20version%20of%20its%20app%20for%20teens%20in%202023.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20company%20has%20integrated%20rides%20for%20young%20people%20into%20its%20broader%20offering.%20It%20now%20lets%20parents%20request%20rides%20for%20their%20kids%20as%20well%20as%20share%20their%20benefits%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-signed-users-up-uber-one-subscription-without-consent-ftc-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20One%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20paid%20subscription%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Khosrowshahi%20said%20at%20an%20investor%20conference%20that%20teens%20were%20among%20the%20%26quot%3Bnew%20demographics%20that%20we're%20going%20after.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20has%20also%20introduced%20a%20streamlined%20version%20of%20its%20app%20for%20seniors%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosrowshahi%20said%20that%20Uber%20doesn't%20keep%20estimates%20of%20how%20many%20people%20%E2%80%94%20teens%20or%20other%20demographic%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20might%20have%20avoided%20buying%20a%20car%20because%20they%20use%20Uber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20did%20say%20on%20the%20podcast%20that%20car%20ownership%20is%20still%20%26quot%3Bthe%20big%20Kahuna%26quot%3B%20that%20Uber%20is%20targeting%20with%20its%20ride-hailing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20gig%20work%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20808-854-4501.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-leading-fewer-teens-to-get-drivers-licenses-ceo-khosrowshahi-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748254861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683075ab6ffb6822ec6153d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-leading-fewer-teens-to-get-drivers-licenses-ceo-khosrowshahi-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uber%20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%20said%20his%20son%20doesn't%20have%20a%20license%2C%20making%20him%20like%20other%20young%20people%20who%20use%20ride-hailing%20instead%20of%20their%20own%20car.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-leading-fewer-teens-to-get-drivers-licenses-ceo-khosrowshahi-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There's%20a%20CEO%20su