p%3EThe%20threat%20an%20autonomous%20AI%20poses%20to%20humanity%20has%20long%20been%20a%20concern%20for%20those%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20developing%20the%20technology%20(and%20fans%20of%20science%20fiction).%20Safety%20and%20its%20benefit%20to%20humanity%20are%20at%20the%20core%20of%20OpenAI's%20mission%2C%20for%20example.%20But%20as%20pressure%20from%20investors%20rises%20to%20justify%20their%20enormous%20financial%20stakes%2C%20some%20engineers%20and%20executives%20have%20raised%20concerns%20that%20AI%20companies%20are%20prioritizing%20the%20release%20of%20new%20products%20over%20ensuring%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanother-openai-employee-quits-over-safety-concerns-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etop%20officials%20have%20left%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20the%20company's%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cofounder-agi-coming-fast-needs-limits-john-schulman-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommitment%20to%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20month%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20it%20would%20consider%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-safety-policy-gpt4-1-employee-criticism-musk-lawsuit-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelaxing%20its%20safety%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0if%20%26quot%3Banother%20frontier%20AI%20developer%20releases%20a%20high-risk%20system%20without%20comparable%20safeguards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-says-ai-risks-are-being-overlooked-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDario%20Amodei%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20recently%20that%20while%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20are%20big%2C%20the%20risks%20are%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20our%20responsible%20scaling%20policy%2C%20it's%20nothing%20but%20AI%2C%20autonomy%2C%20and%20CBRN%