e%20of%20new%20technologies%20to%20allow%20new%20generations%20to%20share%20in%20the%20enjoyment%20of%20those%20legacies%20and%20renowned%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20union%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20must%20protect%20our%20right%20to%20bargain%20terms%20and%20conditions%20around%20uses%20of%20voice%20that%20replace%20the%20work%20of%20our%20members%2C%20including%20those%20who%20previously%20did%20the%20work%20of%20matching%20Darth%20Vader's%20iconic%20rhythm%20and%20tone%20in%20video%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-sag-aftra-actors-wga-writers-unions-strike-hollywood%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewent%20on%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%20for%20148%20days%20in%20part%20to%20force%20studios%20to%20negotiate%20terms%20around%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223cfbb405-575d-48d4-9439-a807c45c6a3c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20potential%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20risks%2C%20there's%20little%20stopping%20AI's%20advancement.%20And%20players%20have%20so%20far%20given%20the%20AI-powered%20Darth%20Vader%20in%20%26quot%3BFortnite%26quot%3B%20positive%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Amyoony%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BFortnite%26quot%3B%20YouTuber%20with%20more%20than%208%20million%20subscribers%2C%20said%20in%20a%20video%20that%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bnever%20seen%20this%20many%20people%26quot%3B%20in%20one%20place%20in%20the%20game%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmyoony%20said%20Epic%20Games%20seemed%20to%20give%20Darth%20Vader%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20about%20in-game%20players.%20It%20even%20knew%20about%20his%20buyable%20%26quot%3Bskin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDarth%20Vader%20had%20that%20information%20and%20knew%20a%20lot%20about%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20character%20has%20had%20some%20hiccups%2C%20the%20bot%20is%20an%20early%20example%20of%20what's%20possible.%20Generative%20AI%20opens%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20of%20immersive%20experiences%20for%20gamers%2C%20one%20where%20characters%20talk%20back%20to%20players%20in%20natural%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20popular%20franchises%3Cspan%3E%2C%20like%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcall-of-duty-activision-ai-in-some-games-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BCall%20of%20Duty%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0are%20experimenting%20with%20using%20AI%20to%20develop%20their%20games.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOther%20studios%20are%20working%20on%20tech%20that%20can%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Emeasure%20a%20player's%20emotions%20and%20convey%20that%20emotion%20to%20non-player%20characters%2C%20who%20then%20use%20AI%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20generating%20real-time%20dialogue%20that%20responds%20to%20player%20emotions%2C%20to%20dynamically%20altering%20game%20environments%20or%20creating%20custom%20assets%2C%20our%20fusion%20of%20affective%20computing%20and%20generative%20AI%20brings%20gaming%20to%20life%20in%20ways%20never%20before%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Ovomind%2C%20a%20GenAI%20company%20working%20to%20develop%20AI%20for%20video%20games%2C%20says%20in%20a%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Disney%20and%20Epic%20Games%2C%20the%20AI-powered%20Darth%20Vader%20in%20%26quot%3BFortnite%26quot%3B%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20what%20will%20likely%20be%20significant%20gaming%20advancements%2C%20all%20the%20result%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisney%2C%20Lucasfilm%2C%20and%20Epic%20Games%20are%20honored%20to%20bring%20his%20voice%20to%20Fortnite%20for%20millions%20of%20players%20to%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20how%20we%20responsibly%20embrace%20emerging%20technologies%20to%20expand%20storytelling%20while%20keeping%20people%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20creative